column.name: task_id
column.Comment: 任务名称,每次作业运行生成新任务

column.name: execution_source
column.Comment: 作业执行来源。可选值为NORMAL_TRIGGER, MISFIRE, FAILOVER

column.name: slave_id
column.Comment: 执行作业服务器的名称，Lite版本为服务器的IP地址，Cloud版本为Mesos执行机主键

column.name: source
column.Comment: 任务执行源，可选值为CLOUD_SCHEDULER, CLOUD_EXECUTOR, LITE_EXECUTOR

column.name: execution_type
column.Comment: 任务执行类型，可选值为NORMAL_TRIGGER, MISFIRE, FAILOVER

column.name: sharding_item
column.Comment: 分片项集合，多个分片项以逗号分隔

column.name: state
column.Comment: 任务执行状态，可选值为TASK_STAGING, TASK_RUNNING, TASK_FINISHED, TASK_KILLED, TASK_LOST, TASK_FAILED, TASK_ERROR

column.name: job_class
column.Comment: 作业实现类，需实现ElasticJob接口

column.name: misfire
column.Comment: 是否开启错过任务重新执行

column.name: failover
column.Comment: 是否开启任务执行失效转移

column.name: jms_type
column.Comment: 消息类型，与queen名枚举对应

column.name: status
column.Comment: 消息状态，与消息状态枚举对应
